{"tid":1494793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「警察，去自殺、去自殺」","createTime":"2019-08-21T19:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:34:33.000Z","uid":34047,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ab958db8dc81a37d27867a1583f7f932bf7687d0","tid":1494793,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:17:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/1094495067293073?view=permalink&amp;id=2395955837146983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1094495067293073%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D2395955837146983&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=972e83fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/1094495067293073?view=permalink&amp;id=2395955837146983</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察，去自殺、去自殺」<br />\n法警爆自殺潮今年64死 家屬：職業遭污名化<br />\n2019年08月20日<br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)法國警察爆發自殺潮，今年至今已有六十四名警員自殺，單是近日就有八人了結生命，包括三名防暴警察、一名指揮官和一名學堂教官。警察工會說，保護者也需要受到保護，要求當局提供更多的幫助去制止問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　自殺的警察來自全國各地，年齡遍布各階層，許多自殺警察遺下了年幼兒女，最近一宗於上周三發生在阿爾代什省。當局至今未找出接連有警察輕生的具體原因。法國國會在七月公布一項調查，指出警察感到巨大壓力和絕望的原因，包括二〇一五年一月以來的一系列恐怖襲擊，以及去年十一月起連續二十多個周末的「黃背心示威」等，令他們工作過勞。<br />\n<br />\n　　有警察妻子坦言，警察置身當權者和示威者中間，不但要承受壓力與焦慮，還要面對社會上對警察職業的污名化，並批評法國政府不作為，要求得到更多支持。今年四月二十日，「黃背心」第二十三周抗議時，人群中竟出現「警察，去自殺、去自殺」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n　　去年另一份報告指出，法國警察自殺率是百分之三十六，比一般自殺率高。法國政府曾於四月底設立自殺預防機構，但效果不佳。法國去年共有三十五名警察自殺，但今年到七月中已突破去年數字，一個月後更增至六十四人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/sf/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtaousa.com%2Fsf%2F11-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F2465123-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B464%25E6%25AD%25BB%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258C%2596%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=c1ba888c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/sf/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1</a><br />\n<br />\nSuicides Among French Police Rise, With 64 So Far This Year<br />\nAug 18, 2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5654923/french-police-suicides/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5654923%2Ffrench-police-suicides%2F&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=4ef98005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5654923/french-police-suicides/</a>"},{"pid":"b43efa4ea93cdc6051e3b654c68854f0574f634a","tid":1494793,"uid":306337,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"係一位前線巴打,有一個心願想大家幫幫我...<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dHsatT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dHsatT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借位推我嘅一個小心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢個idea唔錯,我今日先係元朗一邊屌空氣,一邊讚班狗老婆緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地幾想打鳩我<br />\n我下次試下嗌 去自殺 先"},{"pid":"2da7bd8f537006ca43f24657613fa178d394e87f","tid":1494793,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43efa4ea93cdc6051e3b654c68854f0574f634a","tid":1494793,"uid":306337,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"係一位前線巴打,有一個心願想大家幫幫我...<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dHsatT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dHsatT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借位推我嘅一個小心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><b